snippet.description:
Davis Cup Tennis Trailer 1993

Official Content From Tengen

Terrific tennis action lets you compete for the championship of a lifetime. Replays and bad calls. Clay, grass, or indoor courts. Training, singles, doubles or tournement modes. Take a friend to court!
